  [Text] The executive commission of the national 
privatization program has postponed to 23 May a decision on the 
Brazilian Lloyd [Brazilian State Shipping Company]. The 
commission took into account a request from the Transportation 
Ministry, which asked for one week for making a proposal. 
  The auctioning of Embraer [Brazilian Aeronautics Company], 
which had been scheduled for 20 May, has been postponed to 4 
August. 

