<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] An Army patrol captured a light Colombian airplane 
after a clash with its crew members. The airplane crashed in the 
crew's effort to escape. 
  According to a Huallaga Front Political Command communique, 
the clash occurred at an illegal airfield in the San Pablo 
district, San Martin Department. The airplane crew members 
escaped but the patrol found 124 kg of cocaine base inside the 
airplane. 

</TEXT>

