  [Text] As of this afternoon, Cuba Vision's viewers have a 
new newscast, one that will allow them to learn, early on, of 
the most important stories that will appear on the National 
Television Newscast [Noticiero Nacional de Television -- NTV]. 
  Every day, Monday through Friday at 1927 [2327 GMT], our 
newsroom personnel will have ready for you a summary of the main 
events making the news in Cuba and in the world. We will thereby 
inform you, quickly and directly, about the subjects that will 
be reported at greater length over NTV at 2000 [0000 GMT]. 

