  [Text] Navy Captain (CG) [Naval Line Corps] Carlos Giani 
will be installed at 1100 today in the naval area of the port of 
Montevideo as sea forces commander and sea fleet command chief 
of staff. He was the commander of the Capitan Miranda training 
ship that was recently refurbished. 
  Giani entered the Naval School on 1 March 1959, graduated on 
21 December 1963 with the rank of midshipman, and was promoted 
to Navy captain on 1 February 1986. 

