  [Text] A few minutes ago Army troops withdrew from the 
Federal Police [PF] premises in Sao Paulo. The order came from 
Brasilia after an agreement whereby the PF personnel, who have 
been on strike for 41 days, committed themselves to performing 
basic services. 

